headline: Palo Alto Networks (NASDAQ:PANW) Reports Q4 CY2025 In Line With Expectations But Stock Drops
summary: Cybersecurity platform provider Palo Alto Networks (NASDAQ:PANW) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 14.9% year on year to $2.59 billion. The company expects next quarter’s revenue to be around $2.94 billion, coming in 13.1% above analysts’ estimates. Its GAAP profit of $0.61 per share was 32.2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
